metadata.name: Celestia
metadata.description:
Celestia is a city fairy whose biggest dream is to travel through the skies, she loves the sea because the stars and moon reflect perfectly, make her feels like home, her favorite scent is the early morning breeze mixed with a little oak.
 
Sometimes she can feel lost because of the duality of feelings between nature and the city but she manages to find herself in the middle of the road.


She'll find her way to the stars, she just need love. 

3000x3000 350dpi
